702424f-b.text:
South 5th Street, east from Marcy Avenue. At the corner (right) is a synagogue and in the background is St. Paul's Evangelical Lutheran Church.
View 2 shows a parking space just west of Marcy Avenue.
P. L. Sperr  September l0, 1941
